Ing '''Bsharri''' (a misusulat muring ''Becharre'', ''Bcharre'', ''Bsharre''; {{lang-ar|بْشَرِّيْ}}), metung yang balen king Lebanon a maki kátas a 1,650 m, a malapit king [[:en:Kadisha Valley|Libis ning Kadisha]]. Atiu king {{coord|34|15|5|N|36|5|50|E}}, king [[Bsharri (Distritu)]], king [[North Governorate]]. Atiu ya mu king lalam ning kakeua o pulu/gubat a [[cedro]] ing Bsharri. Keti ya mibait ing pikabaluan a [[poeta]], [[talapinta]], ampong [[escultor]], i [[Khalil Gibran]], a atin na ngening [[Gibran Museum|museo]] king balen a magparangal kaya.     

Ing Bsharri karinan ne ning balayan da reng tau Fenicia kanitang minunang panaun. Mika santungan la keti deng Cristianong Maronite a  tatakas king pamanalipit kareng kayang kabundukan kanitang kapitung dilanua o siglo AD. Ing [[:en:Kadisha Valley|Libis ning Kadisha]], king lalam ning balen, megi yang centrung espiritual ning Pisamban a Maronite. Balu de reng [[Crusader]] ing balen king lagiung Buissera.

King Lebanon, kilala da la reng memalen ning Bsharri a matapang ampong matapat king tribu. Particular, pikabaluan la king aliwang tonu neng magsalitang Arabu. E anti kareng aliwang dake ning Lebanon, magagamit ya pa murin ing [[:en:Aramaic language|Aramaic]] king Bsharri aniang malibutad na king dilanuang 1800. Uli na niti, masikan ing tonu da reng tubu king Bsharri angga pa ngeni, at pagmaragul dang mayap iti.  

Aniang [[:en:Lebanese civil war|Gerang civil king Lebanon]] (1975&ndash;1990), metung yang baluarti ning pamaglaban da reng Cristiano laban king Syria ing Bsharri. Aniang 1986, i [[Samir Geagea]], a tubu king Bsharri, megi yang pekapun ning pangimut a [[Lebanese Forces]] (LF). Dakal a kayanib ning LF ing miagiag king balen aniang gerang civil. Maralas dong amanuan a talapamingua da reng Maronite king Lebanon deng tubu king Bsharri. 

Mipapaburen ya pa murin king kapamahalan ing balen, at ala yang ospital, universidad, o proyectung munie carera kareng kayang kayanakan, ania mamalis la kareng lakanbalen/ciudad ampo kareng aliwang bansa.

Ngeni, atiu ing balen king metung a labuad a dakal a turista. Mayayakit la keti deng lugal a pupuntalan dang turista, kayabe ne ing Libingan ampong Museong Gibran, ing [[:en:Kadisha Valley|Libis nign Kadisha]], nung nu ya tinuknang i Antonios Torbey antimong ermitaniu king Hermitage of St. Lichaa king lalam king libis; ing Kadisha Grotto, ing kakeuan o kagubatan/pulung [[Cedro ning Dios]], metugn a ski resort, ampo ing Bka'kafra (ing lugal nang kebaitan [[San Charbel]]). 

Atin yang Lebanese [[Red Cross]] First Aid Center ing Bsharri.<ref>[http://www.dm.net.lb/redcross/our_centers.html Our Centers<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>. Also it is home for the "The Maronite Scouts" that started their activities early 2000. Makabasi la murin keti deng "The Maronite Scout" a migumpisa kareng karelang actividad aniang mumunang dake ning 2000.

